Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.68,1:47:09.63,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.80,1:47:10.47,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.64,1:47:11.99,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 你在那裏嗎？
