Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.92,1:49:47.35,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直的愛著你…
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.72,1:49:52.63,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找…
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.88,1:49:55.79,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福吧…
